name: Enforcement
text: [§302A-1136]  Enforcement.  The department shall be charged with the enforcement of sections 302A-1132 to 302A-1135.  Nothing in this section shall relieve any chief of police or police officer of the chief's or officer's responsibility for the enforcement of these sections, but their enforcement shall be subject to the plans and policies of the department. [L 1996, c 89, pt of §2]
